{"schemaVersion":"kfc_portal_schema_v1","generatedAt":"2026-07-21T10:39:33.511233+00:00","type":"article","id":"md_85d1f554d7ca40829a1d","item":{"id":"md_85d1f554d7ca40829a1d","type":"article","title":"货拉拉服务端质量保障之测试策略篇","sourceId":"onenote-web-dom","status":"digested","publishedAt":"2026-06-14T13:21:45Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-14T13:25:44Z","summary":"货拉拉服务端质量保障之测试策略篇 原创 质量保障部 货拉拉技术 ![[assets/09 货拉拉服务端质量保障之测试策略篇 img 06 a2c8cc8305.png]] 2024年08月28日 11:16 广东 作者简介 •代丽，来自货拉拉/技术中心/质量保障部，主要负责货拉拉交易和履约以及资金领域的质量保障和服务端质量体系建设工作。 一、背景与挑战 服务端质量保障是确保服务器端应用程序在开发、部署和运行过程中达到预期性能和可靠性的关键步骤。一个全面的服务端测试策略不仅能提高系统的稳定性和安全性，还能提升用户体验和满意度。 货拉拉服务端整体采用微服务架构，单点服务交互链路呈复杂的发散状： ![[assets/09 货拉拉服务端质量","path":"data/semantic_pipeline_v2/articles/md_85d1f554d7ca40829a1d/raw.md","url":"https://onenote.officeapps.live.com/o/onenoteframe.aspx?ui=zh-CN&rs=zh-CN&wopisrc=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.microsoftpersonalcontent.com%2Fpersonal%2F8ec51c56dea4cf15%2F_vti_bin%2Fwopi.ashx%2Ffolders%2F8EC51C56DEA4CF15!18516&wd=target%28%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%2Eone%7Ca2a9ede0%2De4d1%2Dea48%2D8ca3%2Defd472fbb73e%2F%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%7C9b050cc0%2D833f%2Db14c%2D87f3%2D6e78e4e0e0be%2F%29&wdorigin=NavigationUrl&wdenableroaming=1&mscc=1&wdodb=1&hid=F6F304A2-208B-7000-08E3-F6B0EAFBD165.0&uih=onedrivecom&wdlcid=zh-CN&dchat=1&sc=%7B%22pmo%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fonedrive.live.com%22%2C%22pmshare%22%3Atrue%7D&wdhostclicktime=1774846116780&jsapi=1&jsapiver=v1&newsession=1&corrid=9a6bdb53-8f72-a4b5-b974-03f97866ca62&usid=9a6bdb53-8f72-a4b5-b974-03f97866ca62&sftc=1&sams=1&cac=1&sfp=1&hch=1&hwfh=1&uihit=docaspx&muv=1&wdredirectionreason=Force_SingleStepBoot&rct=Normal&ctp=LeastProtected&afdflight=52"}}